></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1200" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/816bfdb0-5191-11ee-bfeb-00bdcbdb0684" width="2000"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Apple]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Still from an Apple marketing video about the new Double Tap gesture in the Watch Series 0]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Double Tap]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Apple is ditching leather to make its products more sustainable]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>苹果公司在今天的主题演讲中花了很多时间谈论其环保诚意，其中一部分原因是它将不再销售皮革配件，包括 iPhone 手机壳和 Apple Watch 表带等产品。该公司指出，虽然皮革在表带等产品中很受欢迎，但它对环境有严重影响，特别是在苹果公司的规模下。</p><p>相反，苹果公司推出了一款名为 FineWoven 的新产品，它将取代其皮带。从视觉上看，它们确实与过去销售的皮革表带非常相似——皮革环和“现代带扣”款式仍然可用，只是采用了这种新的 FineWoven 材料。我们还没有接触过 iPhone，但想必我们也会听说该设备的 FineWoven 保护壳。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>苹果长期以来一直与爱马仕在 Apple Watch 领域建立合作伙伴关系，爱马仕是一家以高端时尚产品（包括各种皮革产品）而闻名的公司。合作还将继续，但爱马仕表带今后也不会是皮革的。看起来它们将由定制的爱马仕帆布、橡胶和其他纺织品制成。</p><p><em>发展...</em></p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-event-2023-live-updates-on-the-new-iphone-15-160001658.html"><em>在这里</em></a><em>关注 Apple “Wonderlust” 活动的所有现场新闻</em><em>。</em></p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/apple-is-removing-leather-from-all-its-products-for-environmental-reasons-173559661.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/apple-is-removing-leather-from-all-its-products-for-environmental-reasons-173559661.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 6c924a61-c1d7-47d7-8844-0b9aa66a2072</guid><dc:creator>内森·英格拉汉姆</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Tue, 12 Sep 2023 17:35:59 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1694540428</ingested><modified> 2023-09-12T17:40:34+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Information Technology]]></category><category><![CDATA[Handheld & Connected Devices]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Nathan Ingraham]]></category><media:content height="1102" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/99d60840-5192-11ee-a4fe-edde2907f086" width="1960"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1102" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/99d60840-5192-11ee-a4fe-edde2907f086" width="1960"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Apple]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Apple FineWoven bands]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Apple FineWoven bands]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Apple Watch Series 9 can handle Siri requests without your iPhone]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>现在是九月，空气中弥漫着秋天的气息，学校又开学了，苹果刚刚发布了新款 Apple Watch。今年， <a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-event-2023-live-updates-on-the-new-iphone-15-160001658.html">该公司展示了</a>Apple Watch Series 9。Series 9 采用了新的处理器、S9 芯片和四核神经引擎，承诺 18 小时的电池续航时间和整体性能提升。在软件方面，watchOS 10 有望成为 Apple Watch 历史上最大的 UI 改革，重新关注小部件，以及大量应用程序和输入更新。</p><p> Series 9 现已开始接受订购，预计于 9 月 22 日上市。起价 399 美元。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>神经引擎支持离线 Siri 访问，这意味着您无需将 iPhone 放在附近即可与 Series 9 上的 Apple 数字助理交互。同样，Series 9 上的听写准确度比 Series 8 高 25%。该引擎还处理人工智能任务的速度是上一次迭代的两倍，并且支持新的手势。 Series 9 GPU 比 Series 8 快 30%，它使用第二代超宽带芯片，可为其他 UWB 设备解锁精确的物体定位。新型号的最大亮度高达 2000 尼特，是 Series 8 的两倍。</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/double-tap-adds-versatile-gesture-control-to-the-apple-watch-series-9-and-apple-watch-ultra-2-173610798.html">新的双击手势</a>允许佩戴者通过快速连续地将拇指和食指放在一起来控制手表的一些功能，而无需触摸屏幕。双击可激活应用程序中的主按钮，因此可用于使用相机遥控器拍照、接听和接听电话、播放和暂停音乐、停止计时器以及其他基本操作。 Double-tap 将在 10 月份的软件更新中推出。</p><p> Apple 宣称 Series 9 是其首款碳中和产品，这意味着精选的表壳和表带组合是碳中和的。这是该公司实现到 2030 年在整个业务、制造供应链和产品生命周期实现碳中和的目标的第一步。</p><p>通过<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/the-apple-watch-embraces-widgets-again-in-watchos-10-180838970.html">watchOS 10</a> ，苹果正在回归其可穿戴设备的根源。最初的 Apple Watch UI 围绕 Glances 展开，它提供了小部件轮播和其他功能，但该公司最终过渡到应用程序优先的 UI。 WatchOS 10 再次将小部件置于前端和中心位置，其风格类似于现有的 Siri 表盘。旋转数字表冠会打开一个智能小部件堆栈，计时器、秒表和播客播放器等应用程序在使用时将填充为小部件。</p><p> watchOS 10 的其他升级包括查看 FaceTime 视频消息和加入 Group FaceTime 音频、在骑行过程中跟踪功率和心率数据以及使用数字表冠在 Mindativity 应用程序中更新您的情绪状态的功能。软件更新还为指南针应用程序添加了有用的功能，包括一个会自动落在您上次有蜂窝连接的地方附近的图钉，这在远足和露营时特别有用。 watchOS 10 的物理控制也发生了变化——按侧面按钮打开控制中心，双击数字表冠即可查看最近使用的应用程序。</p><p>当然，您不需要闪亮的新系列 9 即可利用这些新功能。 watchOS 10 更新将在 Apple Watch Series 4 及更高版本上提供。</p><p> Apple Watch 多年来没有出现重大的设计更新，自 2020 年 Series 6 以来，每个新型号的硬件和软件都发生了增量变化。这使得 Series 9 中的 S9 处理器升级引人注目。再加上 watchOS 10 的推出，对于 Apple Watch 佩戴者来说，这是令人兴奋的一年。</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-event-2023-live-updates-on-the-new-iphone-15-160001658.html"><em>在这里</em></a><em>关注 Apple “Wonderlust” 活动的所有现场新闻</em><em>。</em></p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/apple-watch-series-9-can-handle-siri-requests-without-your-iphone-171920001.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/apple-watch-series-9-can-handle-siri-requests-without-your-iphone-171920001.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 646667a2-ef6f-4f0c-9856-554bef33612f</guid><dc:creator>杰西卡·康迪特</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Tue, 12 Sep 2023 17:19:20 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1694541435</ingested><modified> 2023-09-12T17:57:22+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Information Technology]]></category><category><![CDATA[Software]]></category><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Jessica Conditt]]></category><media:content height="1200" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/7d7707b0-518f-11ee-9f7e-4813ed0438c8" width="2000"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1200" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/7d7707b0-518f-11ee-9f7e-4813ed0438c8" width="2000"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Apple]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Apple Watch Series 9]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Apple Watch Series 9]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Kontrol S-Series MK3 hands-on: A high-end MIDI keyboard for the Native Instruments faithful]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p> Native Instruments 的<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2014-09-02-native-instruments-komplete-keyboards.html">Kontrol S 系列</a>MIDI 键盘因其坚固的结构以及与<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/komplete-now-native-instruments-subscription-160441774.html">Kontakt</a>和<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2019-06-27-native-instruments-releases-massive-x-software-synth.html">Massive X</a>等公司乐器的紧密集成而深受制作人和音乐家的喜爱。今年，控制器进行了相当重大的升级，将硬件推向了新的高度，并加强了与公司旗舰软件的集成。</p><p>从外观上看， <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Sweetwater Sound;elmt:;cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=e54dc56f-69db-417f-9610-572a1a179058&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Sweetwater+Sound&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAY9AIGEh3cXOfnZ7HC4S6wy5BjfZkGKVnD7EpoQ656Lm&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sweetwater.com%2Fstore%2Fdetail%2FKontS3-49--native-instruments-kontrol-s49-mk3-49-key-smart-keyboard-controller" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.sweetwater.com/store/detail/KontS3-49--native-instruments-kontrol-s49-mk3-49-key-smart-keyboard-controller">Kontrol S MK3</a>几乎没有什么明显的区别。其一，鲜明的哑光黑色美感已经被淡化了一些。不要误会我的意思，它仍然是一个主要是黑色的东西，但有一些额外的灯光和彩色标签已添加到一些按钮上。触摸条也被移到了音调轮和调制轮上方，这似乎是一个微小的调整，但大大提高了可玩性。它经常会成为障碍，很多 Native Instruments 的客户都抱怨这一点，所以很高兴看到该公司倾听反馈。 </p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/0dd09350-5184-11ee-8efd-27c4bd5be1d9" data-crop-orig-src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/0dd09350-5184-11ee-8efd-27c4bd5be1d9" style="height:1467px;width:2200px;" alt="Native Instruments Kontrol S 系列 MK3" data-uuid="734c2b9a-8984-3d67-848c-8dec81ff8f2c"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">特伦斯·奥布莱恩/Engadget</div></figure><p>另一个明显的区别是屏幕。 MK2 有两个小但实用的屏幕，而 MK3 有一个大型高分辨率屏幕。它明亮、清晰，易于从任何角度观看。许多图形和用户界面元素也进行了更新，以利用新的显示屏。您无法在键盘上完成 DAW 中的<em>所有操作</em>（就像使用<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/the-new-ableton-push-is-an-mpe-enabled-standalone-music-production-powerhouse-081118260.html">Ableton Push</a>那样），但您可以在<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/native-instruments-launches-komplete-14-music-production-suite-171804393.html">Komplete Kontrol</a>中完成几乎所有操作。该屏幕允许您浏览所有 Native Instruments 插件和声音包，甚至许多第三方 VST（例如来自 Arturia 的 VST），并配有插图。然后更改参数，并提供视觉反馈，直到获得所需的声音。</p><p>如果您不想处理 Komplete Kontrol 的额外开销，键盘可以直接点击<a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2020-03-20-native-instruments-analog-dreams-free.html">Kontakt 7</a> 。坦白说我更喜欢这个。虽然能够直接从键盘浏览、加载和调整预设，无论乐器如何，这都很好，但可能有点让人不知所措。当您通过 Komplete Kontrol 中间人时，加载 Kontakt 音库会出现更多的延迟。 （而且在我四年前的戴尔电脑上，它们打开的速度足够慢。） </p><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/0dd74a11-5184-11ee-9f5c-c015faef152e" data-crop-orig-src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/0dd74a11-5184-11ee-9f5c-c015faef152e" style="height:1237px;width:2200px;" alt="Native Instruments Kontrol S 系列 MK3" data-uuid="ab1e0219-bd9b-3594-91d0-b7b27b66837b"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">特伦斯·奥布莱恩/Engadget</div></figure><p>屏幕下方的八个旋钮可让您根据加载的仪器快速访问许多参数。在 Kontakt 中，还有额外的灵活性，因为它们可以根据预设而变化，默认情况下会加载性能模式。这些是被认为对于实时调整最重要的八个参数。但是，您可以通过点击屏幕上方的按钮切换到编辑模式来更深入地了解，在编辑模式中您可以翻阅完整的选项集并获得真正详细的补丁设计。所有这一切都归功于新的NKS 2.0（Native Kontrol Standard）平台。</p><p> S 系列的其他两个主要变化不太明显。对于一个人来说，有一个新的一体式外壳，可能不会产生任何实际差异，但确实给一代带来了稍微更坚固的感觉。电容式编码器以及音调轮和调制轮也均由机加工铝制成。这是一款感觉值得专业工作室使用的键盘。 </p><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/0ddc7a30-5184-11ee-9dcf-d05e957f8669" data-crop-orig-src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/0ddc7a30-5184-11ee-9dcf-d05e957f8669" style="height:1237px;width:2200px;" alt="Native Instruments Kontrol S 系列 MK3" data-uuid="2895882a-ff39-3307-8e6e-d9ad8ab52284"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">特伦斯·奥布莱恩/Engadget</div></figure><p>更令人兴奋的是与 Fatar 合作开发的新键座，为 Kontrol 系列带来了和弦触后功能。虽然目前还没有很多 Native Instruments 的插件充分利用这一点，但它确实为产品阵容增加了一些面向未来的功能。随着 MPE 越来越受欢迎，公司必须采取一些措施来跟上时代的步伐。</p><p>感觉也很棒。我测试了 Kontrol S49，它和它的稍大的兄弟 S61 一样，有一个半配重键座。触后的行程很短，但令人满意，而且总的来说，它对演奏的反应自然，让您可以从演奏中获得很多细微差别。然而，S88 将配备全锤击键盘，这可能对严肃的钢琴演奏者更有吸引力。 </p><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/0dd72300-5184-11ee-bb7b-66a509701864" data-crop-orig-src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/0dd72300-5184-11ee-bb7b-66a509701864" style="height:1237px;width:2200px;" alt="Native Instruments Kontrol S 系列 MK3" data-uuid="122a2ce2-2647-33c7-a24a-5cba8a837e66"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">特伦斯·奥布莱恩/Engadget</div></figure><p>最后，值得注意的是，船上还有大量的连接。显然，有通过 USB-C 的 MIDI，但也有专用的五针 MIDI 输入和输出，以及四个踏板输入插孔（一个延音、一个表情和两个可分配）。</p><p> <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Native Instruments;elmt:;cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=2d4d4627-d3cf-4cf6-8315-dfc17770e1d3&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Native+Instruments&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5uYXRpdmUtaW5zdHJ1bWVudHMuY29tL2VuL2NhdGFsb2cvaGFyZHdhcmUva2V5Ym9hcmRzLyIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiOWZlMGQ3NDItNjUyZC00NGYxLWJkYjktZDFjNDVjZTZhOTRjIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAfiryIh1IoXdfRu8eyrtibKjAn2V8qwaWpUc8Al3DLPN&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.native-instruments.com%2Fen%2Fcatalog%2Fhardware%2Fkeyboards%2F" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.native-instruments.com/en/catalog/hardware/keyboards/">Native Instruments Kontrol S 系列 MK3</a>键盘现已开始接受预订，S49 起价为<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Sweetwater Sound;elmt:;cpos:9;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=e54dc56f-69db-417f-9610-572a1a179058&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Sweetwater+Sound&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAY9AIGEh3cXOfnZ7HC4S6wy5BjfZkGKVnD7EpoQ656Lm&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sweetwater.com%2Fstore%2Fdetail%2FKontS3-49--native-instruments-kontrol-s49-mk3-49-key-smart-keyboard-controller" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.sweetwater.com/store/detail/KontS3-49--native-instruments-kontrol-s49-mk3-49-key-smart-keyboard-controller">749 美元</a>，S61 起价为<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Sweetwater Sound;elmt:;cpos:10;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=e54dc56f-69db-417f-9610-572a1a179058&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Sweetwater+Sound&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAYV2_gnJyGhqhCP0CBSyu9qtpIHS0mvwezuOpSdK_Ctu&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sweetwater.com%2Fstore%2Fdetail%2FKontS3-61--native-instruments-kontrol-s61-mk3-61-key-smart-keyboard-controller" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.sweetwater.com/store/detail/KontS3-61--native-instruments-kontrol-s61-mk3-61-key-smart-keyboard-controller">849 美元</a>，S88 起价为<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Sweetwater Sound;elmt:;cpos:11;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=e54dc56f-69db-417f-9610-572a1a179058&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Sweetwater+Sound&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAASPzNl0IxXEdRrrZY1-mpr0DtnDqedFddkLjkfsoj_nA&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sweetwater.com%2Fstore%2Fdetail%2FKontS3-88--native-instruments-kontrol-s88-mk3-88-key-smart-keyboard-controller" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.sweetwater.com/store/detail/KontS3-88--native-instruments-kontrol-s88-mk3-88-key-smart-keyboard-controller">1,299 美元</a>。这三款产品预计将于 10 月份某个时候开始发货。 </p><p><core-commerce id="458a089799ff49f4ad8bb1cc46c91cfe" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p></p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/kontrol-s-series-mk3-hands-on-a-high-end-midi-keyboard-for-the-native-instruments-faithful-162055627 .html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/kontrol-s-series-mk3-hands-on-a-high-end-midi-keyboard-for-the-native-instruments-faithful-162055627.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 9fe0d742-652d-44f1-bdb9-d1c45ce6a94c</guid><dc:creator>泰伦斯·奥布莱恩</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Tue, 12 Sep 2023 16:20:55 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1694536084</ingested><modified> 2023-09-12T16:28:10+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Terrence O&#39;Brien]]></category><media:content height="1237" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/0dd72302-5184-11ee-b3e5-97120e8fb774" width="2200"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1237" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/0dd72302-5184-11ee-b3e5-97120e8fb774" width="2200"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Terrence O'Brien / Engadget]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Native Instruments Kontrol S-Series MK3]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Native Instruments Kontrol S-Series MK3]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[The best tablets for 2023]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>迄今为止，平板电脑世界还没有发生太多变化。您有各种尺寸的<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-ipads-how-to-pick-the-best-apple-tablet-for-you-150054066.html">iPad</a> 、更新的<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/samsung-galaxy-tab-s9-ultra-review-a-little-too-big-a-little-too-expensive-150026015.html">三星 Galaxy S9 系列</a>平板电脑以及一些可行的更便宜的设备和<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-e-ink-tablet-130037939.html">电子墨水平板电脑</a>可供选择。虽然最近没有很多突破性的版本，但如果您正在市场上购买新平板电脑或正在寻找笔记本电脑的替代品，您仍然有很多出色的平板电脑可供选择。让我们来详细分析一下在决定购买新设备之前应该考虑什么，以及我们当前精选的最佳平板电脑。</p><h2>哪个操作系统适合我？</h2><p>在您开始考虑特定设备之前，请考虑您的新平板电脑将如何与您已有的小工具相适应，以及您打算如何使用它。例如，如果您家里的每个人都使用 Mac 和 iPhone，那么即使您被新款<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/samsung-galaxy-tab-s9-ultra-review-a-little-too-big-a-little-too-expensive-150026015.html">Galaxy Tab S9 Ultra</a>上的 14.6 英寸大屏幕所吸引，购买 Android 平板电脑可能也没有多大意义。 <a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/samsung-galaxy-tab-s9-ultra-review-a-little-too-big-a-little-too-expensive-150026015.html">。</a>对于拥有大量购买的视频和音乐库的人来说，这会加倍，而在切换平台后可能更难访问这些库。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>另一个考虑因素是您将要做的工作类型。这是因为，虽然大多数现代平板电脑都擅长浏览网站或玩游戏，但 iPadOS 和 Windows 11 等一些操作系统比 Android 甚至 Chrome OS 更能支持多任务处理和提高工作效率。软件的情况也类似，因为虽然大多数流行的应用程序和游戏都可以在 Apple 的 App Store 和 Google 的 Play 商店中找到，但更专业的软件可能只在 Windows 或 macOS 等桌面平台上得到适当的支持。</p><h2>我应该选择什么尺寸的屏幕？</h2><p>确定最适合您的屏幕尺寸还与您打算从事的工作（或娱乐）类型有关。更大的显示屏可以更轻松地并排查看两个应用程序，大屏幕还可以提供更身临其境的电影观看体验。但与此同时，平板电脑越大，您就越不愿意移动它。这意味着您不仅要评估您的工作空间（即，如果您有一张桌子，或者计划在沙发甚至床上工作），您还需要考虑如何设备将适合您的日常生活或通勤（如果您有的话）。</p><h2>潜在配件</h2><p>最后，您需要考虑计划使用的任何附加组件或配件，其中包括可拆卸键盘到外部麦克风或手写笔等。好消息是，当今许多最好的平板电脑都提供某种键盘配件，这使得设备的功能更像二合一，而不仅仅是内容消费设备。一些平板电脑还具有支持可扩展存储的 microSD 卡插槽或可选的 4G 或 5G 连接等功能，这对经常旅行的人来说是一个真正的福音。如果您打算主要使用平板电脑进行工作，您可能需要一个 USB 集线器来连接所有您喜爱的外围设备。</p><h2>我们如何测试</h2><p>在评估不同的平板电脑时，我们最看重的是一些重要的因素：稳定的性能、良好的屏幕和较长的电池寿命。对于性能，我们运行了一些综合测试，例如 Geekbench 6，同时还执行了许多现实世界的用例，例如编辑照片和玩游戏。由于平板电脑通常用作混合设备，我们还考虑了多任务处理和在各种应用程序之间快速切换是多么容易。设备的响应速度越快越好。</p><p>由于平板电脑的显示屏是一个至关重要的组件，因此我们还会查看各种内容来衡量亮度、色域和动态范围等内容。重要的是要考虑 OLED 等各种面板类型之间的差异，OLED 通常会产生更丰富的色彩和出色的对比度，但可能不如 Mini LED 显示器那么明亮。最近，刷新率已成为一个越来越重要的规格，因为 90Hz 和 120Hz 屏幕可以使滚动更流畅，图形在游戏中显得更清晰。</p><p>我们还考虑平板电脑的设计（包括尺寸、重量和防水性）、连接性（WiFi、蓝牙、NFC、5G 等）以及手写笔支持或作为辅助显示器的功能等特殊功能。这是因为，虽然平板电脑在过去经常被视为内容消费设备，但对于很多人来说，Surface Pro 和 iPad Pro 等高端设备完全有能力<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/the-best-2-in-1-laptops-for-2023-155052641.html">取代笔记本电脑</a>。</p><p>最后，我们通过运行标准的本地视频耗尽测试来测试电池寿命，其中包括从 100% 循环播放单个视频，直到电量耗尽。理想情况下，平板电脑应该能够持续一整个工作日，但更长的运行时间总是受欢迎的。</p><h2>最佳平板电脑：Apple iPad Pro </h2><p><core-commerce id="ee244226ac8f41a6a6963b8dee9b2ab6" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9zdG9yZXMvcGFnZS80NUUxNDM0QS1GRDU4LTQwQTctQkMxNC1BNjk4Q0QzNkRGN0M_&amp;signature=AQAAAZtPDfg5pd1RjnTecI9phynDaRaaLjiKYx-zC0Bi7XBO&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fstores%2Fpage%2F45E1434A-FD58-40A7-BC14-A698CD36DF7C%3F_encoding%3DUTF8%26store_ref%3DSB_A08778292RIRQ4ZUH855M%26pd_rd_plhdr%3Dt%26aaxitk%3D094f12dbd533746035ea73fa272aab9f%26hsa_cr_id%3D4219929570501%26lp_asins%3DB09323PCV7%2CB09QHXTHYZ%26lp_query%3Dipad%2Bpro%26lp_slot%3Dauto-sparkle-hsa-tetris%26pd_rd_w%3D3YSC5%26pf_rd_p%3D488a18be-6d86-4de0-8607-bd4ea4b560f3%26pd_rd_wg%3DwZIHz%26pf_rd_r%3DJC6ZAVKVCP3XWFPMPVQA%26pd_rd_r%3D831f2cf4-13f7-48da-869d-440099b8f100%26">iPad Pro</a>搭载与 MacBook 相同的 Apple M2 芯片，是最好的 iPad，也是当今可以买到的最精良的平板电脑之一。它有<a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-ipad-pro-2022-m2-review-140026198-140026510-140026377-140026181.html">两种尺寸</a>（11 英寸和 12.9 英寸），可与一系列配件配合使用，包括<a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAQM2L5ruY23Krn3s2MmnmYL8u37RxJgD8pauGA_NzKoT&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FApple-MU8F2AM-A-Pencil-Generation%2Fdp%2FB07K1WWBJK">Apple Pencil</a>和极其有用（但价格昂贵） <a data-i13n="cpos:9;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAfOWeDl4x8J2EiBAT7Jt9cqgbcb4KnrS1Q-lCqXXxzJY&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FMagic-Keyboard-11-inch-iPad-Generation%2Fdp%2FB0863BQJMS">的妙控键盘</a>。得益于 120Hz ProMotion mini-LED 显示屏，无论您是在观看电影还是在创建幻灯片演示，iPad Pro 的屏幕都拥有强大的亮度和流畅的视觉效果。最新版本的 iPadOS 还使苹果最优质的平板电脑成为功能更加强大的工作设备，增加了用于在应用程序之间快速切换的新侧边栏、用于 Safari 的更强大的类似桌面的 UI 以及各种新工具栏。</p><p>主要缺点是，带有 128GB 存储空间的 11 英寸基本型号起售价为<a data-i13n="cpos:10;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9BcHBsZS0xMS1pbmNoLWlQYWQtUHJvLVdpLUZpLTEyOEdCL2RwL0IwQkpMQktNVjg_dGg9MSZ0YWc9Z2RndDBjLXAtby1mdC0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiMjcxOTRhN2QtODQzNS00ODAyLThlYzAtM2JmZGI3ZDk5Y2JhIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAXQgYt8j7AxYhJYRafgADHYeD-wqY-cVcykEBAhoz4e0&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FApple-11-inch-iPad-Pro-Wi-Fi-128GB%2Fdp%2FB0BJLBKMV8%3Fth%3D1">800 美元</a>，苹果 iPad Pro 并不便宜，而且这还是在你添加蜂窝连接或键盘等任何额外功能之前。但考虑到最新的 iPad Pro 很可能比你当前的笔记本电脑更强大，因此苹果的顶级平板电脑没有什么是它无法处理的。</p><p>最后一点是，如果你喜欢 iPad Pro，但想要更便宜一点的东西，还有<a data-i13n="cpos:11;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMDlWM0pIM1hTP3RoPTEmdGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tZnQtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6IjI3MTk0YTdkLTg0MzUtNDgwMi04ZWMwLTNiZmRiN2Q5OWNiYSJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAS2WWBMEcHsYY6z8Lo7EEAi9R4bDYi8pAxtclAQdog9v&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB09V3JH3XS%3Fth%3D1">第五代 iPad Air。</a>这款产品由 M1 芯片组供电，但支持 Apple Pencil 和可选的 5G 连接。而且屏幕尺寸为 10.9 英寸，与较小的 iPad Pro 尺寸基本相同。主要区别在于<a data-i13n="cpos:12;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-ipad-air-5th-generation-review-130019050.html">iPad Air 的</a>显示屏不太亮，并且不支持 120Hz 刷新率。但如果你同意的话，第五代 iPad Air 本质上是一款 iPad Pro，屏幕不那么精美，起价为 599 美元，而不是 799 美元。</p><ul><li><p><strong>显示屏：</strong> 11 英寸或 12.9 英寸 mini-LED Liquid Retina 面板，支持 ProMotion (120Hz)</p></li><li><p><strong>处理器：</strong>苹果M2</p></li><li><p><strong>存储：</strong> 128GB 至 2TB</p></li><li><p><strong>电池寿命：</strong>长达 10 小时</p></li><li><p><strong>摄像头：</strong> 12MP超广角前置摄像头、12MP广角和10MP超广角后置摄像头</p></li></ul><p><a data-i13n="cpos:13;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-ipad-pro-2022-m2-review-140026198-140026510-140026377-140026181.html"><strong>阅读我们对 Apple iPad Pro 的完整评论</strong></a></p><h2>最佳安卓平板电脑：三星 Galaxy Tab S9 系列</h2><p><core-commerce id="782bf5303363481eaa43c48cba37f921" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>与去年一样，三星推出了三种屏幕尺寸的<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:14;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwQzRCQkYyM0Y_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tZnQtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6IjI3MTk0YTdkLTg0MzUtNDgwMi04ZWMwLTNiZmRiN2Q5OWNiYSJ9&amp;signature=AQAAASlMseUrrgLjfcBWmGEuX6T-fzdGGmR5v3IvibkjjL_o&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0C4BBF23F" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0C4BBF23F">Galaxy Tab S9</a> ：11、12.4 和 14.6 英寸。我们只评测了 14.6 英寸 Galaxy Tab S9 Ultra，但除屏幕尺寸外，所有三款平板电脑均具有相同的规格，并且相机阵列略有差异。虽然<a data-i13n="cpos:15;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/samsung-galaxy-tab-s9-ultra-review-a-little-too-big-a-little-too-expensive-150026015.html">S9 Ultra</a>太大了，不太适合长时间握在手里，但 11 英寸和 12.4 英寸型号是 Android 平板电脑的最佳选择，它们具有出色的屏幕和随附的 S Pen 手写笔，非常适合您。反应灵敏。</p><p>三星今年在 Galaxy Tab S9 系列上提高了 RAM 和处理器。高通的 Snapdragon 8 Gen 2 芯片功能强大，足以满足我想做的一切，而且 12GB 的 RAM 比去年平板电脑上的 8GB 有了很大的提升。这些平板电脑的防水防尘等级甚至达到了 IP68，因此，如果您想带着 S9 去洗澡看电影，则不必担心它滑入浴缸时会损坏。添加一个坚固的配件生态系统，包括多种不同的键盘盖和 Dex 多任务处理模式，S9 也可以成为强大的生产力工具。</p><p>真正出色的 Android 平板电脑凤毛麟角，谷歌凭借自己的<a data-i13n="cpos:16;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/google-pixel-tablet-review-clever-accessories-transform-an-unexciting-tablet-070147119.html">Pixel 平板电脑</a>重新回到了这个领域。虽然作为一款平板电脑，它的吸引力不足以将 Galaxy Tab S9 挤下榜首，但对于那些想要一款既可以用作平板电脑又可以用作智能显示器的设备的人来说，它可能是一个有趣的选择。诚然，它的光芒不如后者，这使得谷歌将底座纳入 500 美元的价格中是一件好事。还有一个售价 80 美元的 Pixel 平板电脑保护壳，它增加了一个非常有用的支架，当您不想连接设备但仍想支撑它时，您可以使用它。</p><ul><li><p><strong>显示屏：</strong> 11英寸LCD、12.4英寸或14.6英寸Super AMOLED</p></li><li><p><strong>处理器：</strong>高通 Snapdragon 8 Gen 2</p></li><li><p><strong>存储：</strong>高达 1TB（取决于型号）</p></li><li><p><strong>电池寿命：</strong>长达 9 小时</p></li><li><p><strong>摄像头：</strong> S9：13MP后置、12MP超宽前置 / S9+：13MP + 8MP超宽后置、12MP超宽前置 / S9 Ultra：13MP + 8MP超宽后置、12MP + 12MP超宽前置</p></li></ul><p><a data-i13n="cpos:17;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/samsung-galaxy-tab-s9-ultra-review-a-little-too-big-a-little-too-expensive-150026015.html"><strong>阅读我们对三星 Galaxy Tab S9 Ultra 的完整评论</strong></a></p><h2>最佳 Windows 平板电脑：Microsoft Surface Pro 9 </h2><p><core-commerce id="3698902d0d2b4ebc9d4eabf7f5fede11" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>虽然大多数人认为微软的 Surface Pro 设备是二合一产品线，因为它们没有配备键盘（您需要单独购买），但从技术上讲，这使它们成为平板电脑。 But don&#39;t be fooled, because thanks to Windows 11 and support for a range of 12h-gen Intel processors, Microsoft&#39;s Surface Pros are designed for productivity.</p><p> The latest <a data-i13n="cpos:18;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/surface-pro-9-5g-review-sq3-arm-173012304.html">Surface Pro 9</a> has a beautiful display with a smooth 120Hz refresh rate and improved stereo speakers, while the inclusion of an IR facial recognition camera allows you to log in to the system in a snap. Another nice bonus is that unlike a lot of tablets, the Surface Pro 9&#39;s SSD is user accessible, allowing you to upgrade its storage yourself whenever you want. And thanks to improvements in Windows 11, the Surface Pro 9 is better suited to life as a tablet without ever needing to attach a smart keyboard thanks to larger app icons and more touch-friendly controls.</p><ul><li><p> <strong>Display:</strong> 13-inch or 15-inch PixelSense touchscreen</p></li><li><p> <strong>Processor:</strong> Microsoft SQ3 or Intel Evo i5/i7</p></li><li><p> <strong>Storage:</strong> 128GB to 1TB</p></li><li><p> <strong>Battery life:</strong> Up to 15.5 hours</p></li><li><p> <strong>Camera:</strong> 1080p Windows Hello front camera, 10MP rear camera</p></li></ul><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:19;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/surface-pro-9-5g-review-sq3-arm-173012304.html"><strong>Read our full review of the Microsoft Surface Pro 9</strong></a></p><h2> Best budget tablet: Apple 10.2-inch iPad </h2><p><core-commerce id="a4a882527db54c78ab3342445c581429" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> If you just want a simple tablet for a reasonable price, it&#39;s hard to go wrong with the standard Apple iPad. Starting at $329, the <a data-i13n="cpos:20;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS8yMDIxLUFwcGxlLTEwLTItaW5jaC1pUGFkLVdpLUZpL2RwL0IwOUc5RlBIWTY_dGg9MSZ0YWc9Z2RndDBjLXAtby1mdC0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiMjcxOTRhN2QtODQzNS00ODAyLThlYzAtM2JmZGI3ZDk5Y2JhIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAbQhIP9FjMGJWqkn3lLBkaXjW19aCcW0qFHMnHSyrO44&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2F2021-Apple-10-2-inch-iPad-Wi-Fi%2Fdp%2FB09G9FPHY6%3Fth%3D1">basic iPad</a> has a 10.2-inch display with good brightness (500 nits) and a relatively speedy A13 Bionic chip. It&#39;s also the last <a data-i13n="cpos:21;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-ipad-9th-generation-review-143045685.html">iPad</a> that still features an old-school Touch ID home button.</p><p> After being refreshed last year, the ninth-gen iPad got updated features including Apple Pencil support, improved cameras (in front and back) and double the base storage (64GB, up from 32GB). And just like its more expensive siblings, this budget tablet is available in a WiFi-only model or with optional 4G LTE cellular connectivity. The entry-level iPad is also the cheapest device Apple sells that gives you access to the App Store, which makes it a good multimedia device and a handy way of managing your media library across your other Apple devices at an affordable price.</p><ul><li><p> <strong>Display:</strong> 10.2-inch Retina display</p></li><li><p> <strong>Processor:</strong> A13 Bionic</p></li><li><p> <strong>Storage:</strong> 64GB, 256GB</p></li><li><p> <strong>Battery life:</strong> 10-14 hours</p></li><li><p> <strong>Camera:</strong> 12MP ultra wide front camera, 8MP wide rear camera</p></li></ul><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:22;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-ipad-9th-generation-review-143045685.html"><strong>Read our full review of the Apple 10.2-inch iPad</strong></a></p><h2> Best tablet for kids: Amazon Fire HD 10 Kids Pro </h2><p><core-commerce id="f9c02adfb5124e8cb2dbcd9148b0fc60" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> If you&#39;re in the market for a new tablet for your child, the Amazon <a data-i13n="cpos:23;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAASI1U3QGkUzBxCBRYIjuoUChRqke7VI_7caSgT6Va8rC&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FFire-HD-10-Kids-Pro-tablet%2Fdp%2FB08F5LWB6R%3F">Fire HD 10 Kids Pro</a> is the easy pick, especially for first time users. Starting at $200, it&#39;s the cheapest tablet on this list, and unlike more adult-oriented fare, it comes with an included “kid-proof” case and a two-year warranty. Amazon says if your kid breaks the tablet, the company will replace it for free.</p><p> Other useful add-ins include a free one-year subscription to <a data-i13n="cpos:24;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9mdHUvaG9tZT90YWc9Z2RndDBjLXAtby1mdC0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiMjcxOTRhN2QtODQzNS00ODAyLThlYzAtM2JmZGI3ZDk5Y2JhIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAfODhNwr9p8pRZl46j1xsXwovmziZd8p1uBnK_MB0DzR&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fftu%2Fhome%3F">Amazon Kids+</a> , which unlocks more than 20,000 games, books and apps designed for children. There&#39;s also a handy dashboard for parents that allows you to set time limits, content filters and educational goals. And even though its 3GB of RAM and 32GB of base storage aren&#39;t much, its 1080p display is plenty sharp and it has a microSD card slot for expandable storage. And if you want a slightly smaller and more affordable option, there&#39;s the $140 <a data-i13n="cpos:25;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMDhINVFYM1lGP3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLWZ0LTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiIyNzE5NGE3ZC04NDM1LTQ4MDItOGVjMC0zYmZkYjdkOTljYmEifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAdVLPL7Pmz8OAZHKO-TwGgpRhxCcMRlM228fasGRs5fu&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB08H5QX3YF%3F">Amazon Fire HD 8 Kids Pro</a> too.</p><ul><li><p> <strong>Display:</strong> 10.1-inch 1080p display</p></li><li><p> <strong>Processor:</strong> 2.0 GHz octa-core processor</p></li><li><p> <strong>Storage:</strong> 32GB, 64Gb (expandable up to 1TB)</p></li><li><p> <strong>Battery life:</strong> Up to 12 hours</p></li><li><p> <strong>Camera:</strong> 2MP front camera, 5MP rear camera</p></li></ul><h2>常见问题解答</h2><h3>What is the best brand for tablets?</h3><p> The best brand for tablets is really the brand you feel most comfortable with. We recommend taking stock of the gadgets you already have — do you live in the Apple ecosystem already? An iPad might be best for you then. Do you have a Samsung phone? If so, a Galaxy Tab will likely be the most convenient choice. There is no one &quot;best brand&quot; for tablets; you&#39;ll find good options made by companies including Apple, Google, Samsung, Microsoft and Amazon.</p><h3> Can a tablet replace a laptop?</h3><p> It&#39;s possible for a tablet to replace a laptop, but you&#39;ll need a few accessories to truly make the experience as close as possible to that of a traditional notebook. A keyboard is a must, be it a keyboard case or a Bluetooth accessory that you keep with you. Some keyboard cases, like apple&#39;s Magic Keyboard for the iPad, have a built-in trackpad, which will be more ergonomic than tapping on your tablet&#39;s screen for input. Additionally, you could go one step further and use a wireless mouse that connects via Bluetooth to your tablet. If you&#39;re primarily looking for a tablet to replace your laptop, consider buying a <a data-i13n="cpos:26;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/the-best-2-in-1-laptops-for-2023-155052641.html">2-in-1 laptop</a> since those systems typically consist of high-powered tablets that are designed to work well with (and without) keyboards.</p> This article originally appeared on Engadget at https://www.engadget.com/best-tablets-150026056.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/best-tablets-150026056.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 27194a7d-8435-4802-8ec0-3bfdb7d99cba</guid><dc:creator>萨姆·卢瑟福</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Tue, 12 Sep 2023 16:15:29 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1694535329</ingested><modified> 2023-09-12T16:15:38+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Consumer Discretionary]]></category><category><![CDATA[Tablets]]></category><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[Handheld & Connected Devices]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Sam Rutherford]]></category><media:content height="1000" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2022-03/a016ca50-9fc3-11ec-bfdd-f179728c5eac" width="1998"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1000" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2022-03/a016ca50-9fc3-11ec-bfdd-f179728c5eac" width="1998"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Engadget]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Apple's iPad Pro, Microsoft's Surface Pro 8 and the Samsung Galaxy Tab S8+ are some of the best tablets on the market today]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[The best tablets of 2022]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[JackRabbit's XG e-bike adds more range, power, fun and expense]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p> In a world of generic electric bikes, the JackRabbit is hard to ignore. The micro, pedal-free ride blends the convenience of a scooter with the sitdown comfort of a bicycle. We <a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/jack-rabbit-ebike-scooter-review-144537677.html">loved the original</a> , but there was plenty of room for improvement. That room has been dramatically reduced with the unveiling of the JackRabbit XG — a newer, more powerful and slightly (just slightly) bigger version available starting today.</p><p> The XG initially looks very similar to the “OG” (as it has since been dubbed) that came before it. What you will notice is that it sports a more conventional diamond-style frame. There are also two batteries this time around for up to 20 miles of range (double the original). As mentioned earlier, the wheelbase is a shade longer, but only by an inch or two. The result is a more refined bike with not only more range but, thanks to a new 500W motor, more power for going up hills with the same 20 mph max speed.</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p> The quality-of-life enhancements also extend beyond extra power and range. The JackRabbit XG comes with an actual bike computer so you can see real time speed, trip length and a more refined battery life gauge. Before, the only feedback you had for anything were three LEDs to indicate remaining power. Additionally, there are new all-metal footpegs, which is great as the original used rubber “shoes” on its pegs and they easily fell off — I lost both within two short rides.</p><p> The addition of the extra battery, combined with that new motor are what really makes the JackRabbit XG feel like an improvement on the original. I stated in my review that the battery life was perhaps on the shorter side and if you ever ran out of juice, like I once did, it wasn&#39;t a very fun time getting back home on, effectively, an adult balance bike. Thankfully, with double the amount of cells, the XG now reaches up to, and maybe even beyond 20 miles of normal usage putting it well on par with what you&#39;d expect from a scooter. (There are no pedals here, so that range is motor-only.) </p><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/5426a280-516c-11ee-bbd9-cb818297b2b9" data-crop-orig-src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/5426a280-516c-11ee-bbd9-cb818297b2b9" style="height:1244px;width:1868px;" alt="A close up of the Jackrabbit e-bike&#39;s handlebar-mounted ride computer." data-uuid="e9f53ca6-33a8-3638-ba31-6e6d7aba7a7a"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit"> Photo by James Trew / Engadget</div></figure><p> One of the first things you noticed when you rode the original was the higher center of gravity which gave the JackRabbit a “lively” riding experience. Thankfully, the XG feels a lot more stable and doesn&#39;t seem to feature any of the twitchy physics at higher speeds. And thanks to the three power modes, you have more control over the maximum speed (and thus range and ride feel) of the bike.</p><p> Naturally, that extra battery and longer frame add a bit of heft. The OG model weighed in at 24 pounds, while the XG adds another eight to that. You can still easily lift the bike with one hand though, and a dash up the subway stairs with it is still perfectly manageable. By keeping with the same battery as the OG, upgraders might even have some spares ready, but also the double battery bay means you can ride on just one cell if needed, or if you just fancy a lighter ride with less range. Thankfully, the batteries no longer require a key to unlock them for swapping out, with new permanent clips on the underside of the XG instead, which is much easier and saves having to carry another, easily losable, key.</p><p> Some smaller details show how the JackRabbit is maturing. For example, the bike now comes with powered front and back lights which connect to a new power port on the side. There&#39;s also a front brake now to augment the rear one so you won&#39;t have to pull a rad slide in certain strong braking situations. That said, there are a couple of other listed features that are perhaps more creative on the marketing side than practical for the user. For one there&#39;s a “walk mode” — which typically has the bike roll itself along slowly as you stroll. But here that mode is achieved not by holding down a button to engage the throttle slightly, instead you loosen the handlebars, rotate them 90 degrees (so that the bike is “thin”) and Jackrabbit&#39;s “walk mode” is “activated.” That said, the same process does easily allow for tidy storage of the bike. </p><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/88ec4f10-516c-11ee-bf7e-8407d1de7de7" data-crop-orig-src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/88ec4f10-516c-11ee-bf7e-8407d1de7de7" style="height:1333px;width:2000px;" alt="A close up of the rear fat-tire of the Jackrabbit e-bike." data-uuid="0b5f8786-e088-3823-bbbe-9abd1ef2563c"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit"> Photo by James Trew / Engadget</div></figure><p> It&#39;s in the riding that the XG comes to life. The OG model would pull away when you pressed the accelerator, but the new model requires you to push off first, much like on a scooter. It&#39;s a minor change, but one that does stop the bike pulling away from you if you accidentally activate the throttle. In “high” mode, you don&#39;t need to push off to start moving, so if that&#39;s what you prefer you can keep it in that setting. Having the three power modes is a welcome way of moderating battery usage without having to be as judicious with the accelerator. I won&#39;t lie though, “high” is the most fun and that&#39;s where I find myself keeping it now that it sports the extra range.</p><p> The OG model had a few rough edges, but was a fun alternative to scooters or small e-bikes. The XG feels much more refined and practical with all the major pain points addressed with very little tradeoff — though it&#39;s a shade larger and heavier making it just that much less convenient than a foldable scooter. With all these changes though comes a much higher price tag. The original was $1,200 when we wrote about it but has since dropped back to $1,000. The XG <a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://jackrabbit.bike/">will cost $1,750</a> at launch.</p><p> That&#39;s a decent step up, but it bests its younger sibling in every conceivable way. That also puts it up in the same price range as many regular e-bikes. If you&#39;re considering the XG purely as an alternative to a scooter then it&#39;s clearly a pricier option. If, however, you want the flexibility of a bike that can perk up your daily commute and go on adventures that scooters can&#39;t, the JackRabbit XG suddenly seems much more attractive.</p> This article originally appeared on Engadget at https://www.engadget.com/jackrabbits-xg-e-bike-adds-more-range-power-fun-and-expense-160038972.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/jackrabbits-xg-e-bike-adds-more-range-power-fun-and-expense-160038972.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> f2e60265-8f74-4581-95d1-a268b2e0fc5f</guid><dc:creator> James Trew</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Tue, 12 Sep 2023 16:00:38 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1694535520</ingested><modified> 2023-09-12T16:18:47+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Automotive Industry]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[